{"tid":1671204,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我地紮鐵3兄弟不求同年同月同日同分同秒生","createTime":"2019-10-23T10:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T10:53:31.000Z","uid":176858,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d637f1e4e236cd50491c096f613fcae1362d467","tid":1671204,"uid":176858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kucE7X1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkucE7X1.jpg&h=c391ed12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地紮鐵3兄弟不求同年同月同日同分同秒生<br />\n只求同年同月同日同分同秒死 <br />\n撩我地皮既 唔理對家係1個定100個<br />\n我地就只得3個<br />\n我老豆因為我做左古惑仔打9我<br />\n我地3兄弟就連我老豆都濕一獲<br />\n呢啲就係好兄弟 邊個打我我地實打番佢 <br />\n親生老豆都無面比 <br />\n我地屁股都紋撚埋身 <br />\n以示忠貞生係3兄弟既人 死係3兄弟既鬼<br />\n無女屌個陣我地會為兄弟出賣自己個口同屎忽 <br />\n我地都唔介意 為兄弟 含撚無悔 感性說話唔多講 <br />\n兄弟在心中😘 #兄弟 #手足"},{"pid":"536eb41ad007c90ac6faa0701f39c3ae622ea0ed","tid":1671204,"uid":280934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThis thread is"},{"pid":"899debe4ff7eb7247aa918bf4b1886917377d2f5","tid":1671204,"uid":266336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"536eb41ad007c90ac6faa0701f39c3ae622ea0ed","tid":1671204,"uid":280934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThis thread is"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Good</span></span>"},{"pid":"60a5504a09344408f2c90a22eca5e34bf1a7c9f8","tid":1671204,"uid":49861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"顛"},{"pid":"f0b70c84a20c75ff4b8f97c4201f336e6252a8fc","tid":1671204,"uid":15605,"like":4,"dislik